Dear {!RW_EOI__c.RW_Primary_First_Name__c} {!RW_EOI__c.RW_Primary_Last_Name__c},

This is with reference to your {!EOINumber}. We are glad to inform you that we have received the {!paymentMode} of Rs {!Amount} from your end towards EOI.

The details of your payment are
Bank Name:{!BankName}
Instrument Number : {!PaymentReferenceNumber}
Date : {!Date}
Amount : {!Amount}

You may call on {!SMPhoneNumber} for any assistance.  

Regards,
Runwal Group
